# 🌐 Mehar's Portfolio Website

This is my personal **portfolio website** built using **HTML5**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It showcases my skills, projects, and provides a way to connect with me.

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Fully responsive design  
- ✅ Clean and modern UI  
- ✅ Navigation bar with smooth scrolling  
- ✅ Hover effects using Tailwind  
- ✅ Typing animation on homepage using JavaScript  
- ✅ Mobile-friendly layout  
- ✅ Deployed via GitHub

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

portfolio/
│
├── portfolio.html
├── output.css
├── style.css
├── js/
│ └── script.js
├── images/
│ └── (your images here)
├── package.json
├── package-lock.json
└── README.md

## 🧰 Built With

- [HTML5](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/HTML5)  
- [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)  
- [JavaScript](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript)  
- [Git & GitHub](https://github.com)

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/mehar-khan0786/portfolio.git
Open the folder and launch portfolio.html in your browser.


If you're modifying Tailwind styles, run:

bash
npx tailwindcss -i ./style.css -o ./output.css --watch


